{{Use mdy dates|date=July 2016}} {{Infobox award | name = SCTV Awards | image = | imagesize = | caption = | description = Outstanding achievement for Indonesian entertainment industry | country = [[Indonesia]] | reward = | year = 2001 | year2 = | website = {{URL|liputan6.com/sctvawards/|Liputan6.com: SCTV Awards}} | network = [[SCTV (Indonesia)|SCTV]] | runtime = | previous = }}
The '''SCTV Awards''' are annual Indonesian awards that are presented by [[SCTV (Indonesia)|SCTV]], which recognize popularity in the [[television]] industry, and which correspond to the [[SCTV Music Awards]] (for music). The annual show was first held on August 24, 2001.
