==Voting System== The show are voted in by [[SCTV (Indonesia)|SCTV]] audiences throughout Indonesia and therefore reflect the popular choices of a significant portion of the television viewing public in the country.
==Awards categories== Awards are presented in several categories, including Famous Lead Role Actress, Famous Lead Role Actor, Famous Supporting Role Actor, Famous Supporting Role Actress, Famous Presenter, Famous Singer, Famous Group Band, Famous Advertisement, and Famous Program. The Lifetime Achievement Award is presented to individuals with lifetime dedication to the entertainment industry.
In 2009, the show introduced the Famous Supporting Role Actor and Famous Supporting Role Actress categories.
